text: Castiel is a former municipality in the district of Plessur in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. On 1 January 2013 the former municipalities of Castiel, Calfreisen, Langwies, Lüen, Molinis, Peist and St. Peter-Pagig merged into the municipality of Arosa. ==Other websites== * Official Website * Category:Former municipalities of Graubünden
title: Castiel, Switzerland
